======================================================================
MODEL 1: All Fish — Wells Interaction + Harvest + Year RE
n = 404 fish across 20 return years
======================================================================

Model 1 Summary:
 Family: bernoulli 
  Links: mu = logit 
Formula: EntiatDetected ~ wells_interaction + harvest_open + (1 | ReturnYearFactor) 
   Data: fish_AB (Number of observations: 404) 
  Draws: 4 chains, each with iter = 4500; warmup = 1500; thin = 1;
         total post-warmup draws = 12000

Multilevel Hyperparameters:
~ReturnYearFactor (Number of levels: 20) 
              Estimate Est.Error l-95% CI u-95% CI Rhat Bulk_ESS Tail_ESS
sd(Intercept)     0.73      0.31     0.18     1.39 1.00     2948     3133

Regression Coefficients:
                  Estimate Est.Error l-95% CI u-95% CI Rhat Bulk_ESS Tail_ESS
Intercept             2.32      0.46     1.44     3.24 1.00     9004     7947
wells_interaction    -1.39      0.27    -1.94    -0.87 1.00    15283     8366
harvest_open         -0.31      0.48    -1.27     0.59 1.00     7396     7171

Draws were sampled using sampling(NUTS). For each parameter, Bulk_ESS
and Tail_ESS are effective sample size measures, and Rhat is the potential
scale reduction factor on split chains (at convergence, Rhat = 1).

--- Model 1 Results ---
Wells Interaction:
  beta_mean = -1.394  (OR = 0.248)
  95% HDI   [-1.950, -0.882]
  P(beta > 0) = 0.0000  [i.e. P(Wells INCREASES return)]
  P(beta < 0) = 1.0000  [i.e. P(Wells DECREASES return)]

Harvest Status (Open vs Closed):
  beta_mean = -0.306  (OR = 0.736)
  95% HDI   [-1.271, 0.592]
  P(beta > 0) = 0.2599

Year-level variability:
  sigma_year = 0.727 (mean)

Diagnostics (fixed effects):
  Rhat range:    [1.000, 1.000]
  Bulk ESS range: [7396, 15283]

